<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>[GYM NAME] | Elite Fitness Vadodara</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles - Dark Theme for Gyms */
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #111; 
            color: #fff; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
        }
        h1, h2, h3 { 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            margin: 0; 
        }
        .container { 
            width: 90%; 
            max-width: 1100px; 
            margin: auto; 
            padding: 0 20px; 
        }
        
        /* Navigation / Header */
        header { 
            background: #000; 
            padding: 20px 0; 
            border-bottom: 3px solid #e53e3e; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        header h2 { 
            color: #e53e3e; 
            letter-spacing: 2px; 
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        /* I've linked a high-quality stock photo of a gym directly from Unsplash so it looks real immediately */
        .hero { 
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.8), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534438327276-14e5300c3a48?q=80&w=1470&auto=format&fit=crop') no-repeat center center/cover; 
            padding: 120px 0; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .hero h1 { 
            font-size: 3.5rem; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000; 
        }
        .hero p { 
            font-size: 1.2rem; 
            margin-bottom: 30px; 
            color: #ccc;
        }
        .btn { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: #e53e3e; 
            color: #fff; 
            padding: 15px 30px; 
            font-size: 1.2rem; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            transition: 0.3s; 
        }
        .btn:hover { 
            background: #c53030; 
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features { 
            padding: 80px 0; 
            background: #1a1a1a; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .features-grid { 
            display: flex; 
            gap: 20px; 
            margin-top: 40px; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
        }
        .feature-card { 
            background: #222; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            flex: 1; 
            border-top: 4px solid #e53e3e; 
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #e53e3e;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        /* Schedule Section */
        .schedule { 
            padding: 80px 0; 
            text-align: center; 
            background: #111;
        }
        table { 
            width: 100%; 
            margin-top: 30px; 
            border-collapse: collapse; 
            background: #222; 
        }
        th, td { 
            padding: 15px; 
            border: 1px solid #333; 
        }
        th { 
            background: #e53e3e; 
            color: #fff; 
        }

        /* Lead Capture CTA (The Money Maker) */
        .cta { 
            padding: 80px 0; 
            background: #e53e3e; 
            color: #fff; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .cta h2 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .cta form {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .cta input { 
            padding: 15px; 
            width: 80%; 
            max-width: 250px; 
            margin: 10px; 
            border: none; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .cta button { 
            padding: 15px 30px; 
            background: #000; 
            color: #fff; 
            border: none; 
            font-size: 1.1rem; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .cta button:hover { 
            background: #222; 
        }

        /* Mobile Responsiveness */
        @media(max-width: 768px) {
            .features-grid { 
                flex-direction: column; 
            }
            .hero h1 { 
                font-size: 2.5rem; 
            }
            .cta input {
                width: 100%;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                max-width: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h2>[GYM NAME]</h2>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Stop Making Excuses. Start Making Progress.</h1>
            <p>Vadodara's premier training facility for serious athletes and fitness enthusiasts.</p>
            <a href="#trial" class="btn">Claim Your Free 1-Day Trial</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Why Train With Us?</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Elite Equipment</h3>
                    <p>From heavy lifting platforms to professional-grade cardio machines, we have exactly what you need to push your limits.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Expert Environment</h3>
                    <p>Surround yourself with people who take their training seriously. No distractions, just hard work and results.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Local Community</h3>
                    <p>Join the strongest community in Vadodara. When you walk through our doors, you're here to work.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="schedule">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Training Hours</h2>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Days</th>
                    <th>Hours</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Monday - Saturday</td>
                    <td>6:00 AM - 10:00 PM</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Sunday</td>
                    <td>7:00 AM - 12:00 PM</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="trial" class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Get Your First Workout Free</h2>
            <p>Drop your details below and we will text you your free 1-day guest pass so you can experience the gym for yourself.</p>
            
            <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('LEAD CAPTURED! This is exactly how the website will collect phone numbers and names for you to call and close as new members.');">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Your Full Name" required>
                <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required>
                <button type="submit">Send My Pass</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
